.SH SIGNALS
SIGHUP causes gvmd to rebuild the database with information from the Scanner (openvassd).
.SH EXAMPLES
gvmd --port 1241

Serve GMP clients on port 1241 and connect to an OpenVAS scanner via the default OTP file socket.
